## ğŸ—„ï¸ Database Schema
```sql
-- Automatic SQLite database creation
students (
  student_id PRIMARY KEY,
  full_name, class_name, academic_year,
  date_of_birth, gender, email, phone
)

academic_records (
  record_id PRIMARY KEY,
  student_id, semester, exam_type,
  simple_gpa, weighted_gpa, grade_level
)

subjects (
  student_id, record_id, subject_name,
  score, weight, category, notes
)
```

