## ğŸ› ï¸ Technical Details

### Built With
- **Language**: Python 3.8+
- **Database**: SQLite3
- **Libraries**: Standard library only (no external dependencies!)
  - `dataclasses` - Data modeling
  - `sqlite3` - Database
  - `statistics` - Analytics
  - `json`, `csv` - Export
  - `datetime`, `hashlib` - Utilities

### Architecture
```
grade_management.py
â”œâ”€â”€ Data Models (dataclasses)
â”œâ”€â”€ Database Manager (SQLite)
â”œâ”€â”€ Analytics Engine (Statistics)
â”œâ”€â”€ Export Engine (Multi-format)
â”œâ”€â”€ User Interface (Terminal UI)
â””â”€â”€ Main Application (Controller)
```

